782
00:33:27,705 --> 00:33:28,831
Oh, well,

783
00:33:28,906 --> 00:33:31,500
then neither can I.

784
00:33:31,576 --> 00:33:34,136
That's a lawyer-client
privilege.

785
00:33:39,484 --> 00:33:41,213
But I tell you what.

786
00:33:43,988 --> 00:33:46,252
I made a couple
of phone calls...

787
00:33:46,324 --> 00:33:47,291
Mm-hmm.

788
00:33:47,358 --> 00:33:49,053
Verifying some accounts.

789
00:33:49,127 --> 00:33:51,595
Your mama's
second husband

790
00:33:51,662 --> 00:33:54,028
left her
an enormous fortune.

791
00:33:54,098 --> 00:33:55,429
How big?

792
00:33:55,500 --> 00:33:57,695
Big.

793
00:33:57,769 --> 00:33:59,066
Big.

794
00:33:59,137 --> 00:34:01,264
I hope you're
not meddling, boy.

795
00:34:02,640 --> 00:34:06,269
Mama, wouldn't you just love
