2194
01:41:45,745 --> 01:41:47,372
[Whispers]

2195
01:41:47,447 --> 01:41:48,778
Approach the witness,
Your Honor?

2196
01:41:48,848 --> 01:41:49,780
You may.

2197
01:41:49,849 --> 01:41:51,214
I am baffled,
Miss Lemancyzk,

2198
01:41:51,284 --> 01:41:52,273
because I have
this letter here,

2199
01:41:52,352 --> 01:41:55,253
and it says you quit
for personal reasons.

2200
01:41:55,321 --> 01:41:56,618
The letter is a lie.

2201
01:41:56,689 --> 01:41:58,884
[People Chatter]

2202
01:41:58,958 --> 01:42:00,550
I was fired so the company
