in his presence.

2216
01:42:42,335 --> 01:42:44,303
[Whispering]

2217
01:42:44,370 --> 01:42:45,462
Baylor:
Go on.

2218
01:42:46,873 --> 01:42:48,932
I took the cash...

2219
01:42:50,310 --> 01:42:52,870
and I also signed a letter
saying I would never discuss

2220
01:42:52,946 --> 01:42:54,937
any of my claims files
with anybody.

2221
01:42:55,014 --> 01:42:57,005
lncluding
the Black file?

2222
01:42:57,083 --> 01:42:59,108
Specifically the Black file.

2223
01:42:59,185 --> 01:43:02,814
So you knew that claim
should have been paid?

2224
01:43:04,457 --> 01:43:05,947
Everybody knew...

2225
01:43:07,360 --> 01:43:10,261
but the company
was playing the odds.

2226
01:43:10,330 --> 01:43:11,820
What odds?

2227
01:43:13,232 --> 01:43:16,463
The odds that the insured
would not consult a lawyer.

2228
01:43:16,536 --> 01:43:18,595
[People Chatter]

2229
01:43:21,407 --> 01:43:23,466
[Dot Crying]

2230
01:43:25,011 --> 01:43:27,070
Now, during that time...

2231
01:43:29,349 --> 01:43:32,716
