claims examiner?

2232
01:43:32,785 --> 01:43:33,979
Yes, that's correct.

2233
01:43:34,053 --> 01:43:36,385
During that time, was
there ever an occasion

2234
01:43:36,456 --> 01:43:37,582
when you were given
instructions

2235
01:43:37,657 --> 01:43:40,125
regarding how you should
handle claims?

