gonna go to his wife,

2329
01:47:36,395 --> 01:47:37,327
go to the newspapers.

2330
01:47:37,396 --> 01:47:38,454
And that $10,000,

2331
01:47:38,531 --> 01:47:40,692
that was just a piece
of blackmail, wasn't it?

2332
01:47:40,766 --> 01:47:43,997
A way to extort money
from the company you hated!

2333
01:47:44,070 --> 01:47:45,196
lsn't that right?

2334
01:47:45,271 --> 01:47:46,499
No, that's not true.

2335
01:47:46,572 --> 01:47:48,733
ln fact, your testimony
here today is just a lie.

2336
01:47:48,808 --> 01:47:50,400
