01:47:58,284 --> 01:48:01,412
A woman scorned!

2340
01:48:01,487 --> 01:48:04,456
Your Honor, I move
that all documents

2341
01:48:04,523 --> 01:48:07,686
provided the plaintiff
by Miss Jackie Lemancyzk

2342
01:48:07,760 --> 01:48:09,625
be deemed
stolen work papers

2343
01:48:09,695 --> 01:48:11,458
