from these proceedings.

2344
01:48:19,739 --> 01:48:24,108
Based on the evidence
presently before the court,

2345
01:48:24,176 --> 01:48:25,871
these documents
are inadmissible.

2346
01:48:25,945 --> 01:48:27,003
